<title type="html"><![CDATA[8/4 (Thu)How to break your habit/ Esper to relay Taiwan’s concern over arm sales (Host: Howard)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=640&amp;p=665#p665"><![CDATA[
How to break your habit/ Esper to relay Taiwan’s concern over arm sales (Host: Howard)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-8:00 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-9:00 Session 2: Group Discussion<br /><br />Open discussion and no sub-grouping. No default questions. Here are the rules:<br />1. Please watch/ read the article carefully before you think up questions to ask others and reply someone's question.<br />2. Your question can't be similar or the same as the others'. So, figuring out more questions is highly appreciated.<br />3. There's no discussion in the subgroup, present your thinking impromptu and directly in N minutes. N depends on how many members join the zoom meeting.<br />4. Voltaire once said ,&quot;I disapprove of what you say, but I will defend to the death your right to say it.&quot;<br /><br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session 1: How to break your habit<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/66441">https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/66441</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />Session 2: Esper to relay Taiwan’s concern over arm sales<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2022/07/22/2003782211">https://taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/arc ... 2003782211</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Fri Jul 29, 2022 2:28 pm</p><hr />
